title: Springfield: Illinois' Sangamon County Seat
content:

Springfield is the county seat of Sangamon County, located in the U.S. state of Illinois.

title: Springfield: Illinois' Sixth Largest City
content: As of 2019, Springfield had a population of 10,566, making it the sixth most populous city in Illinois.
